file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  description: URL redirect operations
  title: URL redirects
  version: v3
servers:
- url: https://api.hubapi.com/
tags:
- name: Redirects
paths:
  /cms/v3/url-redirects/:
    get:
      description: Returns all existing URL redirects. Results can be limited and
        filtered by creation or updated date.
      operationId: get-/cms/v3/url-redirects/_getPage
      parameters:
      - description: Only return redirects created on exactly this date.
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: createdAt
        required: false
        schema:
          format: date-time
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: Only return redirects created after this date.
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: createdAfter
        required: false
        schema:
          format: date-time
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: Only return redirects created before this date.
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: createdBefore
        required: false
        schema:
          format: date-time
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: Only return redirects last updated on exactly this date.
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: updatedAt
        required: false
        schema:
          format: date-time
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: Only return redirects last updated after this date.
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: updatedAfter
        required: false
        schema:
          format: date-time
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: Only return redirects last updated before this date.
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: updatedBefore
        required: false
        schema:
          format: date-time
          type: string
        style: form
      - explode: true
        in: query
        name: sort
        required: false
        schema:
          items:
            type: string
          type: array
        style: form
      - explode: true
        in: query
        name: properties
        required: false
        schema:
          items:
            type: string
          type: array
        style: form
      - description: The paging cursor token of the last successfully read resource
          will be returned as the `paging.next.after` JSON property of a paged response
          containing more results.
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: after
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      - explode: true
        in: query
        name: before
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: Maximum number of result per page
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: limit
        required: false
        schema:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        style: form
      - description: Whether to return only results that have been archived.
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: archived
        required: false
        schema:
          type: boolean
        style: form
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              example:
                total: 2
                results:
                - id: "3212223134"
                  createdAt: 2017-07-24T17:24:09.141Z
                  updatedAt: 2017-07-24T17:24:09.141Z
                  routePrefix: http://test.hs-sites.com/(?P<page_slug>.*)
                  destination: http://www.example.online/{page_slug}
                  redirectStyle: 301
                  isOnlyAfterNotFound: true
                  isMatchFullUrl: true
                  isMatchQueryString: false
                  isPattern: false
                  isTrailingSlashOptional: true
                  isProtocolAgnostic: true
                  precedence: 3
                - id: "3212242073"
                  createdAt: 2017-07-25T15:42:06.410Z
                  updatedAt: 2017-07-25T15:42:06.410Z
                  routePrefix: /mytest/(?P<page_slug>.*)
                  destination: /newtest/{page_slug}
                  redirectStyle: 301
                  isOnlyAfterNotFound: true
                  isMatchFullUrl: true
                  isMatchQueryString: false
                  isPattern: false
                  isTrailingSlashOptional: true
                  isProtocolAgnostic: true
                  precedence: 999999993
                paging:
                  next:
                    after: Mg%3D%3D
                    link: https://api.hubspot.com/cms/v3/url-redirects?hapikey&after=Mg%3D%3D
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/CollectionResponseWithTotalUrlMapping'
          description: successful operation
        default:
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
          description: An error occurred.
      security:
      - hapikey: []
      - oauth2_legacy:
        - content
      summary: Get current redirects
      tags:
      - Redirects
    post:
      description: Creates and configures a new URL redirect.
      operationId: post-/cms/v3/url-redirects/_create
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/UrlMappingCreateRequestBody'
        required: false
      responses:
        "201":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/UrlMapping'
          description: successful operation
        default:
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
          description: An error occurred.
      security:
      - hapikey: []
      - oauth2_legacy:
        - content
      summary: Create a redirect
      tags:
      - Redirects
  /cms/v3/url-redirects/{urlRedirectId}:
    delete:
      description: Delete one existing redirect, so it is no longer mapped.
      operationId: delete-/cms/v3/url-redirects/{urlRedirectId}_archive
      parameters:
      - description: The ID of the target redirect.
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: urlRedirectId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "204":
          content: {}
          description: Delete succeeded
        default:
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
          description: An error occurred.
      security:
      - hapikey: []
      - oauth2_legacy:
        - content
      summary: Delete a redirect
      tags:
      - Redirects
    get:
      description: Returns the details for a single existing URL redirect by ID.
      operationId: get-/cms/v3/url-redirects/{urlRedirectId}_getById
      parameters:
      - description: The ID of the target redirect.
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: urlRedirectId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              example:
                id: "3212223134"
                createdAt: 2017-07-24T17:24:09.141Z
                updatedAt: 2017-07-24T17:24:09.141Z
                routePrefix: http://test.hs-sites.com/(?P<page_slug>.*)
                destination: http://www.example.online/{page_slug}
                isOnlyAfterNotFound: true
                isMatchFullUrl: true
                isMatchQueryString: false
                isPattern: false
                isTrailingSlashOptional: true
                isProtocolAgnostic: true
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/UrlMapping'
          description: successful operation
        default:
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
          description: An error occurred.
      security:
      - hapikey: []
      - oauth2_legacy:
        - content
      summary: Get details for a redirect
      tags:
      - Redirects
    patch:
      description: Updates the settings for an existing URL redirect.
      operationId: patch-/cms/v3/url-redirects/{urlRedirectId}_update
      parameters:
      - explode: false
        in: path
        name: urlRedirectId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/UrlMapping'
        required: false
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/UrlMapping'
          description: successful operation
        default:
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
          description: An error occurred.
      security:
      - hapikey: []
      - oauth2_legacy:
        - content
      summary: Update a redirect
      tags:
      - Redirects
components:
  responses:
    Error:
      content:
        '*/*':
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
      description: An error occurred.
  schemas:
    CollectionResponseWithTotalUrlMapping:
      example:
        total: 0
        paging:
          next:
            link: link
            after: after
        results:
        - note: note
          redirectStyle: 9
          isMatchQueryString: true
          isMatchFullUrl: true
          destination: destination
          isPattern: true
          precedence: 2
          internallyCreated: true
          portalId: 1
          cosObjectType: CONTENT
          isProtocolAgnostic: true
          id: 6
          createdById: 2
          isTrailingSlashOptional: true
          isRegex: true
          cdnPurgeEmbargoTime: 7
          created: 5
          contentGroupId: 3
          label: label
          updatedById: 7
          isOnlyAfterNotFound: true
          deletedAt: 4
          routePrefix: routePrefix
          name: name
          updated: 5
        - note: note
          redirectStyle: 9
          isMatchQueryString: true
          isMatchFullUrl: true
          destination: destination
          isPattern: true
          precedence: 2
          internallyCreated: true
          portalId: 1
          cosObjectType: CONTENT
          isProtocolAgnostic: true
          id: 6
          createdById: 2
          isTrailingSlashOptional: true
          isRegex: true
          cdnPurgeEmbargoTime: 7
          created: 5
          contentGroupId: 3
          label: label
          updatedById: 7
          isOnlyAfterNotFound: true
          deletedAt: 4
          routePrefix: routePrefix
          name: name
          updated: 5
      properties:
        total:
          description: The number of available results.
          format: int32
          type: integer
        results:
          description: Matched URLs.
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/UrlMapping'
          type: array
        paging:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Paging'
      required:
      - results
      - total
      type: object
    Error:
      example:
        message: Invalid input (details will vary based on the error)
        correlationId: aeb5f871-7f07-4993-9211-075dc63e7cbf
        category: VALIDATION_ERROR
        links:
          knowledge-base: https://www.hubspot.com/products/service/knowledge-base
      properties:
        message:
          description: A human readable message describing the error along with remediation
            steps where appropriate
          example: An error occurred
          type: string
        correlationId:
          description: A unique identifier for the request. Include this value with
            any error reports or support tickets
          example: aeb5f871-7f07-4993-9211-075dc63e7cbf
          format: uuid
          type: string
        category:
          description: The error category
          type: string
        subCategory:
          description: A specific category that contains more specific detail about
            the error
          type: string
        errors:
          description: further information about the error
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErrorDetail'
          type: array
        context:
          additionalProperties:
            items:
              type: string
            type: array
          description: Context about the error condition
          example:
            invalidPropertyName:
            - propertyValue
            missingScopes:
            - scope1
            - scope2
          type: object
        links:
          additionalProperties:
            type: string
          description: A map of link names to associated URIs containing documentation
            about the error or recommended remediation steps
          type: object
      required:
      - category
      - correlationId
      - message
      type: object
    ErrorDetail:
      properties:
        message:
          description: A human readable message describing the error along with remediation
            steps where appropriate
          type: string
        in:
          description: The name of the field or parameter in which the error was found.
          type: string
        code:
          description: The status code associated with the error detail
          type: string
        subCategory:
          description: A specific category that contains more specific detail about
            the error
          type: string
        context:
          additionalProperties:
            items:
              type: string
            type: array
          description: Context about the error condition
          example:
            missingScopes:
            - scope1
            - scope2
          type: object
      required:
      - message
      type: object
    NextPage:
      example:
        link: link
        after: after
      properties:
        after:
          type: string
        link:
          type: string
      required:
      - after
      type: object
    Paging:
      example:
        next:
          link: link
          after: after
      properties:
        next:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/NextPage'
      type: object
    UrlMapping:
      example:
        note: note
        redirectStyle: 9
        isMatchQueryString: true
        isMatchFullUrl: true
        destination: destination
        isPattern: true
        precedence: 2
        internallyCreated: true
        portalId: 1
        cosObjectType: CONTENT
        isProtocolAgnostic: true
        id: 6
        createdById: 2
        isTrailingSlashOptional: true
        isRegex: true
        cdnPurgeEmbargoTime: 7
        created: 5
        contentGroupId: 3
        label: label
        updatedById: 7
        isOnlyAfterNotFound: true
        deletedAt: 4
        routePrefix: routePrefix
        name: name
        updated: 5
      properties:
        id:
          description: The unique ID of this URL redirect.
          format: int64
          type: integer
        portalId:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        created:
          format: int64
          type: integer
        updated:
          format: int64
          type: integer
        createdById:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        updatedById:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        routePrefix:
          description: The target incoming URL, path, or pattern to match for redirection.
          type: string
        destination:
          description: The destination URL, where the target URL should be redirected
            if it matches the `routePrefix`.
          type: string
        redirectStyle:
          description: 'The type of redirect to create. Options include: 301 (permanent),
            302 (temporary), or 305 (proxy). Find more details [here](https://knowledge.hubspot.com/cos-general/how-to-redirect-a-hubspot-page).'
          format: int32
          type: integer
        contentGroupId:
          format: int64
          type: integer
        isOnlyAfterNotFound:
          description: Whether the URL redirect mapping should apply only if a live
            page on the URL isn't found. If False, the URL redirect mapping will take
            precedence over any existing page.
          type: boolean
        isRegex:
          type: boolean
        isMatchFullUrl:
          description: Whether the `routePrefix` should match on the entire URL, including
            the domain.
          type: boolean
        isMatchQueryString:
          description: Whether the `routePrefix` should match on the entire URL path,
            including the query string.
          type: boolean
        isPattern:
          description: Whether the `routePrefix` should match based on pattern.
          type: boolean
        isTrailingSlashOptional:
          description: Whether a trailing slash will be ignored.
          type: boolean
        isProtocolAgnostic:
          description: Whether the `routePrefix` should match both HTTP and HTTPS
            protocols.
          type: boolean
        name:
          type: string
        precedence:
          description: Used to prioritize URL redirection. If a given URL matches
            more than one redirect, the one with the **lower** precedence will be
            used.
          format: int32
          type: integer
        deletedAt:
          format: int64
          type: integer
        note:
          type: string
        label:
          type: string
        internallyCreated:
          type: boolean
        cosObjectType:
          enum:
          - CONTENT
          - EXTENSION_RESOURCE
          - LAYOUT
          - CUSTOM_WIDGET
          - WIDGET
          - FORM
          - PLACEMENT
          - IMAGE
          - DOMAIN_SETTINGS
          - SITE_SETTINGS
          - EMAIL_ADDRESS
          - WORKFLOW
          - HUBDB_TABLE
          - REDIRECT_URL
          - DESIGN_FOLDER
          - SITE_MAP
          - DOMAIN
          - BLOG
          - FILE
          - FOLDER
          - SITE_MENU
          - THEME
          - CONTENT_GROUP
          - FOLLOW_ME
          - KNOWLEDGE_BASE
          - LIST_MEMBERSHIP
          - CONTACT_MEMBERSHIP
          - PASSWORD_PROTECTED
          - UNRESTRICTED_ACCESS
          - MARKETPLACE_LISTING
          - LAYOUT_SECTION
          - THEME_SETTINGS
          - VIDEO_PLAYER
          - URL_MAPPING
          - KNOWLEDGE_CATEGORY
          - KNOWLEDGE_HOMEPAGE_CATEGORY
          - RAW_ASSET
          - GLOBAL_CONTENT
          - HUBDB_TABLE_ROW
          - BLOG_AUTHOR
          - SERVERLESS_FUNCTION
          - KNOWLEDGE_CATEGORY_TRANSLATION
          type: string
        cdnPurgeEmbargoTime:
          format: int64
          type: integer
      required:
      - cdnPurgeEmbargoTime
      - contentGroupId
      - cosObjectType
      - created
      - createdById
      - deletedAt
      - destination
      - id
      - internallyCreated
      - isMatchFullUrl
      - isMatchQueryString
      - isOnlyAfterNotFound
      - isPattern
      - isProtocolAgnostic
      - isRegex
      - isTrailingSlashOptional
      - label
      - name
      - note
      - portalId
      - precedence
      - redirectStyle
      - routePrefix
      - updated
      - updatedById
      type: object
    UrlMappingCreateRequestBody:
      example:
        isTrailingSlashOptional: true
        redirectStyle: 0
        isMatchQueryString: true
        routePrefix: routePrefix
        isMatchFullUrl: true
        destination: destination
        isProtocolAgnostic: true
        isOnlyAfterNotFound: true
        isPattern: true
        precedence: 6
      properties:
        routePrefix:
          type: string
        destination:
          type: string
        redirectStyle:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        precedence:
          format: int32
          type: integer
        isOnlyAfterNotFound:
          type: boolean
        isMatchFullUrl:
          type: boolean
        isMatchQueryString:
          type: boolean
        isPattern:
          type: boolean
        isTrailingSlashOptional:
          type: boolean
        isProtocolAgnostic:
          type: boolean
      required:
      - destination
      - redirectStyle
      - routePrefix
      type: object
  securitySchemes:
    oauth2_legacy:
      flows:
        authorizationCode:
          authorizationUrl: https://app.hubspot.com/oauth/authorize
          scopes:
            content: Read from and write to my Content
          tokenUrl: https://api.hubapi.com/oauth/v1/token
      type: oauth2
    hapikey:
      in: query
      name: hapikey
      type: apiKey

- PHP
